Package system.core

Class MyVelib

java.lang.Object
system.core.MyVelib
public class MyVelib extends Object
This class defines the characteristics of the myVelib system.

It is composed of the bicycle list, the station list, the user list and a renter.

    MyVelib(int numberOfDockingStation, int numberOfParkingSlotByStation, double initialPopulationProportion, double mecanicalBicycleProportion, double plusStationProportion, double s)
